# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
pytest-cache-files-*/
build/
dist/
.DS_Store

# Personal data — never commit (your eBird life-list export)
MyEBirdData.csv
*MyEBirdData*

# Raw eBird data and large generated stores.
# Reasons: (1) eBird's Terms of Use forbid redistributing the raw dataset, and
# (2) these are huge / regenerable. Ignore everything under data/ EXCEPT the small,
# safe fixtures needed to run the tests: the published taxonomy and the synthetic
# precomputed sample. Everything else (EBD .gz/.txt, sampling files, bar charts,
# .sqlite/.parquet stores, duckdb scratch) stays local.
data/*
!data/taxonomy/
!data/precomputed.csv

# belt-and-suspenders for big artifacts anywhere
*.gz
*.tar
*.zip
*.sqlite
*.parquet
duckdb_tmp/
.tmp/
# raw EBD text dumps at any path (huge; eBird ToU forbids redistribution)
ebd_*.txt
*_relApr-*.txt

# stray per-run diagnostic tables dumped at repo root (regenerable; keep repo clean)
eb_shrinkage_*.csv

# local tooling / vendored skills — not part of the app
skills/
